products.title: Carnival 15 Ochre Roller Blind
products.description: Carnival roller blinds are great for kitchens, bathrooms or offices. At swiftdirectblinds, quality is important to us, so not only does this roller blind made by their expert team and comes with customer-first service, we also provide a five-year guarantee, for extra peace of mind.
